Package: birtir
Title: Render Analysis Scripts to Plain Markdown Reports
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Auðun", "Valborgarson", email = "your@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Runs analysis scripts, captures console output, and writes plain
    Markdown reports. Exported helpers such as md_table() and md_plot() can be
    used directly in scripts, printing previews interactively and writing into
    the active report during render_analysis_md().
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
